---
title: Shrimp Peperonata Pasta with Long Green Pepper
description: Some nights, nothing but a big bowl of pasta will do. (If that’s 3 out of 5 weeknights for you, we totally get it.) This week, our chefs whipped up a delicious, Italian-inspired dish that’s sure to curb the most ferocious carb cravings. This twist on the classic peperonata is brimming with savory long green pepper, sweet shallot, and a rich garlic-and-oregano-flecked tomato sauce with succulent shrimp. For a finishing touch, a sprinkle of chili flakes offers a customizable kick, depending if you seek the heat (or not!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w32-r13-shrimp-peperonata-pasta-70726d3b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/shrimp-peperonata-pasta-5d0ab31c67dfb30014120fad-1db4a998.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shrimp-peperonata-pasta-5d0ab31c67dfb30014120fad
author: HelloFresh
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
